final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First, determine that the green object is the Goal object. Then, align the agent on the horizontal axis (y=8) since the yellow object is at the same y-coordinate. The agent does not need to move in the vertical direction. Next, move the agent to reach the yellow object (x=13) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Pick up the Key by moving into its space. Then, move the agent to align with the cyan object on the horizontal axis (y=8). The agent does not need to move in the vertical direction. Next, move the agent to reach the cyan object (x=18) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=13 and it moved 8 steps right, it must move RIGHT 5 more times. Move onto the cyan object to open the KeyDoor and destroy the Key. Finally, move the agent to align with the green object on the horizontal axis (y=11). The agent needs to move UP 3 times since y=8 and y=11 have a difference of 3. Next, move the agent to reach the goal (x=19) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=18, it must move RIGHT 1 time.
